   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Of Livian barley of the crop of year 7 and 6, in the name of Ptolemaios, his mother being Demetrous, through beasts of Magdola, through Didymos, two donkeys, equal 2. Year 7 and 6, Pachon 26.</ab>
